#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info is a type of documentation. The documents are in a file format called "
"texinfo, and can be read on the command line with the <ulink url=\"info:/info"
"\"><command>info</command></ulink> program."
msgstr ""
"Info je vrsta dokumentacije. Dokumenti so v datotečnem formatu texinfo in se "
"jih da brati iz ukazne vrstice s programom <command>info</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Info KIO worker allows you to read the info pages installed on your "
"system, from within &konqueror;. You can use it very easily:"
msgstr ""
"KIO worker za Info vam omogoča, da lahko berete strani z informacijami, ki "
"so nameščene na vašem računalniku, od znotraj programa &konqueror;. Njegova "
"uporaba je precej enostavna:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>info:</command><replaceable>gcc</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>info:</command><replaceable>gcc</replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This would show you the top level node of the Info documentation for the "
"&gcc; compiler."
msgstr ""
"To vam bo prikazalo vrhnje vozlišče Info dokumentacije za prevajalnik &gcc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info is a &GNU; replacement for <command>man</command>, but is not widely "
"used outside of &GNU; software."
msgstr ""
"Info je &GNU;-jeva zamenjava za <command>man</command>, vendar pa se izven "
"programske opreme &GNU; ne uporablja prav pogosto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can quite easily browse the info documentation you have installed from "
"within the &khelpcenter; application, or you can use the info KIO worker "
"directly from within both &konqueror; and the mini-cli."
msgstr ""
"Po info dokumentaciji, ki ste jo naložili, lahko razmeroma z lahkoto brskate "
"v aplikaciji &khelpcenter;, lahko pa uporabite KIO worker za info neposredno "
"iz programa &konqueror; in majhnega ukaznega okna (mini-cli)."
